    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_GetSets500WhenRootFolderIsUnreadable;dir;req
    ‚ćĚ A directory that exists and is genuinely unreadable (mode 000) passes
    ‚ćĚ CheckFolder as 'ok' - readability is not one of its outcomes - and only
    ‚ćĚ fails inside BuildListingResponse's directory-listing call, which Get's
    ‚ćĚ :Trap 0 turns into a 500.
