      #.AppState.RootFolder‚Üźdir
      req‚ÜźStubReq'/files'
      {}#.Get req
      r‚Üźreq.Response.Status‚Č°500
      {}‚éēSH'chmod 755 ',dir
      3 ‚éēNDELETE dir
